sect1.para:
It would be nice to have this presentation model injected into the view that needs it. For this we can annotate the view in question with some metadata and have Spring Actionscript take care of the rest.<s:VGroup xmlns:fx="http://ns.adobe.com/mxml/2009" xmlns:s="library://ns.adobe.com/flex/spark" xmlns:mx="library://ns.adobe.com/flex/mx"> <fx:Script> <![CDATA[ import my.classes.presentationmodels.MainPresentationModel;
[Inject] public var presentationModel:MainPresentationModel; ]]> </fx:Script> </s:VGroup>
Don't forget to add this compiler switch to the Flex project when using [Inject] metadata: -keep-as3-metadata+=Inject.
